cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.DS, cs.CL

The paper deals with image processing techniques for business card images captured by a cell-phone camera, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. The paper also involves text extraction and segmentation, which are common tasks in information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper involves computational efficiency, which is a common concern in distributed systems (cs.DS).
